      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "POST /ingest                  \u2190 n8n W1 + W2\nPOST /query                   \u2190 Open WebUI\n        (reads LanceDB directly,\n         bypasses ingestion pipeline)\nGET  /sessions\nGET  /sessions/{session_id}\nGET  /speaker-aliases-block   \u2190 n8n W2\nPOST /reindex\nGET  /health\nauth: RETRIEVAL_API_KEY  (single key)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "POST /ingest                  \u2190 n8n W1 + W2\nPOST /query                   \u2190 Open WebUI\n        (reads LanceDB directly,\n         bypasses ingestion pipeline)\nGET  /sessions\nGET  /sessions/{session_id}\nGET  /speaker-aliases-block   \u2190 n8n W2\nPOST /reindex\nGET  /health\nauth: RETRIEVAL_API_KEY  (single key)",
